---
title: Shrimp, Zucchini & Sun-Dried Tomato Risotto with Grape Tomatoes & Parmesan
description: What’s not to love about risotto? It’s luxurious, comforting, and never fails to satisfy. With a reputation for being labor intensive—ours couldn’t be easier! This version begins as classic as can be, with rich veggie stock and the addition of sweet-tart sun-dried tomatoes. It’s finished with zesty spice-roasted zucchini and grape tomatoes, two perfect contrasts to risotto’s creamy richness. For a finishing touch, everything receives a generous sprinkle of Parmesan.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64107b4ba025f0196c0634f2-11867e85.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/64933a213477e872b82f0617.pdf
time required: 40 minutes
course: main course
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/shrimp-zucchini-sun-dried-tomato-risotto-64933a213477e872b82f0617
cuisine: Italian
nutrition:
  calories: 830 kcal
  fat: 32 g
  saturated fat: 15 g
  carbohydrates: 98 g
  sugar: 19 g
